These are Puzzles for 4x5 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-4-1::.
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: water-polo, surfing, cycling, soccer, biathlon
5 different games are played: backgammon, domino, snooker, poker, bridge
There are 5 different favourite colors: light-blue, red, white, fuchsia, turquise
There are 5 different nationalities: british, indonesian, nigerian, spanish, turkish
 1. the nigerian is on the left or right of the person playing bridge##3
 2. the person playing backgammon is in an odd position##4
 3. the person who likes light-blue is on the left of the indonesian##1
 4. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the right of the person who likes fuchsia##1
 5. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left or right of the person playing backgammon##3
 6. the person who likes fuchsia is on the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
 7. the person playing bridge is on the right of the person who likes white##1
 8. the turkish is in an even position##4
 9. the british is on the left or right of the person playing poker##3
10. the person who likes white is the person playing snooker##1
11. the person who likes red is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1
12. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left or right of the person playing backgammon##3
13. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the right of the indonesian##1
14. the turkish is on the left of the person who likes turquise##1
15. the person who likes fuchsia is the person who's sport is soccer##1
16. the person who likes fuchsia is on the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |        2        |     3      |    4     |     5     |
| Sport      | cycling    | water-polo   | soccer     | biathlon      | surfing      |
| Game           | snooker | bridge | backgammon    | poker | domino |
| Color   | white       | light-blue         | fuchsia      | red      | turquise    |
| Nationality   | nigerian    | spanish         | indonesian | turkish  | british   |

