 3. the fan of indie is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 4. the person eating garlic is the person eating garlic##1
 5. the fan of house is on the right of the person who's sport is swimming##1
 6. the fan of r&b is on the right of the fan of indie##1
 7. the person who's sport is soccer is on the far right##1
 8. the manager is on the left or right of the security-guard##3
 9. the fan of classical is the manager##1
10. the person eating orange is the person who's sport is climbing##1
11. the police-officer is the person eating strawberry##1
12. the person who's sport is climbing is between the fisherman and the fan of reggae##2
13. the fan of reggae is on the left or right of the person eating orange##3
14. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the far left or far right##3
15. the person eating strawberry is in an odd position##4
