.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-4-15::.
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: classical, house, soul, country, indie
There are 5 different favourite beverages: sprite, fanta, iced-tea, cola, milk
There are 5 different favourite colors: aquamarine, chestnut, purple, grey, amber
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: baseball, basketball, cricket, sailing, skateboarding
 1. the fan of house is on the right of the person who likes aquamarine##1
 2. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the person who's sport is baseball##3
 3. the person who likes aquamarine is on the left or right of the person who likes purple##3
 4. the person who likes purple is on the right of the fan of classical##1
 5. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person who likes purple##1
 6. the person who's sport is sailing is in an even position##4
 7. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left or right of the person drinking iced-tea##3
 8. the person who likes chestnut is between the person who's sport is cricket and the fan of indie##2
 9. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
10. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the person who likes purple##3
11. the person drinking sprite is in an odd position##4
12. the person who's sport is basketball is on the far right##1
13. the fan of country is on the far right##1
14. the fan of indie is on the far left or far right##3
15. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left or right of the person who likes amber##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |     3     |    4     |     5      |
| Music-Genre          | indie      | soul       | classical | house | country |
| Beverage   | iced-tea       | milk    | cola  | fanta  | sprite |
| Color           | amber         | chestnut | aquamarine      | purple     | grey    |
| Sport         | skateboarding | baseball   | cricket   | sailing  | basketball |

