.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-4-16::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: light-blue, green, amber, lilac, emerald
There are 5 different favourite beverages: water, fanta, soy-milk, lemonade, tea
There 5 different types of food: potato, broccoli, cabbage, garlic, pomegranate
The people use 5 different means of transport: boat, car, helicopter, quad-bike, van
 1. the person driving the quad-bike is the person who likes green##1
 2. the person driving the boat is on the left or right of the person driving the helicopter##3
 3. the person who likes amber is on the left of the person driving the van##1
 4. the person driving the helicopter is the person eating garlic##1
 5. the person who likes green is on the left or right of the person eating broccoli##3
 6. the person who likes green is in an odd position##4
 7. the person who likes lilac is on the left of the person eating cabbage##1
 8. the person eating garlic is the person drinking fanta##1
 9. the person driving the quad-bike is the person eating pomegranate##1
10. the person drinking lemonade is the person eating broccoli##1
11. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
12. the person who likes amber is in the middle##1
13. the person who likes green is on the left of the person who likes emerald##1
14. the person eating garlic is on the left or right of the person who likes emerald##3
15. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person driving the van##1
16. the person drinking water is the person driving the car##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |         2          |     3      |       4        |      5       |
| Color         | green     | emerald | amber | lilac | light-blue      |
| Beverage         | tea     | lemonade               | fanta       | soy-milk     | water       |
| Food       | pomegranate | broccoli              | garlic    | potato        | cabbage |
| Transport   | quad-bike  | boat               | helicopter | van            | car          |

