.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-4-17::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: fanta, iced-tea, milk, mirinda, soy-milk
City: edinburgh, liverpool, colone, new-york, marseilles
5 different pets are kept: bird, cat, ferret, guinea-pig, goldfish
There are 5 different nationalities: thai, british, chinese, brazilian, egyptian
 1. the brazilian is in an odd position##4
 2. the person drinking milk is between the egyptian and the owner of the goldfish##2
 3. the person drinking iced-tea is between the owner of the goldfish and the person traveling to marseilles##2
 4. the owner of the ferret is on the left or right of the owner of the cat##3
 5. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left or right of the person drinking milk##3
 6. the person traveling to colone is the person drinking milk##1
 7. the thai is in an even position##4
 8. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
 9. the person drinking milk is in an even position##4
10. the owner of the cat is on the far right##1
11. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the british##1
12. the person traveling to marseilles is on the right of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
13. the owner of the bird is on the left of the person traveling to new-york##1
14. the person drinking mirinda is the brazilian##1
15. the person drinking mirinda is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |     2      |     3     |    4     |      5      |
| Beverage    | fanta       | milk       | soy-milk  | iced-tea | mirinda     |
| City       | liverpool | colone    | new-york | edinburgh  | marseilles |
| Pet         | guinea-pig     | bird | goldfish     | ferret   | cat    |
| Nationality   | egyptian         | british  | chinese | thai | brazilian        |

