.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-4-18::.
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: zinnia, daisy, aconite, sunflower, lily
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: bluemaster, oliveros, alhambra, fonseca, baccarat
There are 5 different nationalities: argentine, dutch, egyptian, mexican, pakistani
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: july, september, may, april, june
 1. the person who growsdaisy is the pakistani##1
 2. the person who growsaconite is on the left of the dutch##1
 3. the baccarat-smoker is on the left or right of the oliveros-smoker##3
 4. the person who's birthday is in june is the baccarat-smoker##1
 5. the pakistani is on the far left##1
 6. the mexican is in an even position##4
 7. the person who growszinnia is on the right of the egyptian##1
 8. the person who growslily is in an even position##4
 9. the egyptian is the alhambra-smoker##1
10. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the fonseca-smoker##1
11. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the pakistani##1
12. the bluemaster-smoker is on the right of the person who growsaconite##1
13. the person who growssunflower is in the middle##1
14. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left or right of the person who growszinnia##3
15. the person who's birthday is in september is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3      |     4     |     5     |
| Flower         | daisy | lily | sunflower    | aconite     | zinnia   |
| Cigar   | baccarat     | oliveros       | fonseca     | alhambra    | bluemaster     |
| Nationality   | pakistani  | mexican   | argentine  | egyptian  | dutch     |
| Birthday     | june      | july  | april | may | september |

