.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-4-19::.
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: august, may, july, december, january
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: dubstep, folk, gospel, indie, r&b
There are 5 different favourite colors: white, azure, yellow, red, ivory
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: golf, handball, skateboarding, parkour, ice-hockey
 1. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is in an odd position##4
 2. the person who's birthday is in july is the fan of gospel##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in may is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the fan of indie is on the left or right of the person who's sport is handball##3
 5. the person who's sport is golf is on the far right##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left or right of the person who's sport is parkour##3
 7. the fan of dubstep is in the middle##1
 8. the person who likes white is on the left of the person who likes yellow##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in december is the person who likes red##1
10. the person who's sport is handball is on the right of the fan of gospel##1
11. the person who likes white is on the left or right of the person who's sport is golf##3
12. the fan of gospel is on the right of the fan of r&b##1
13. the fan of folk is on the far left or far right##3
14. the person who likes ivory is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |      3      |     4      |     5      |
| Birthday   | may  | july | december | january    | august     |
| Music-Genre   | r&b      | gospel   | dubstep     | indie      | folk       |
| Color   | azure | ivory     | red     | white | yellow    |
| Sport     | ice-hockey   | skateboarding   | handball   | parkour    | golf |

