.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-4-20::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: baking, card-games, rock-climbing, skydiving, writing
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: october, april, january, july, may
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, aconite, azalea, bellflower, begonia
5 different games are played: poker, bridge, domino, whist, go
 1. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the person who growsbellflower##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in january is on the far right##1
 3. the person playing domino is on the left of the person who growsazalea##1
 4. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in may##3
 5. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##3
 7. the person who's hobby is writing is in the middle##1
 8. the person who growsazalea is on the right of the person who growsbegonia##1
 9. the person who growsaconite is the person who's birthday is in october##1
10. the person who growsbellflower is the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
11. the person playing go is in an even position##4
12. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the person playing whist##1
13. the person playing whist is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
14. the person playing poker is in an odd position##4
15. the person who growsballoon-flower is the person playing poker##1
16. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in may##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3      |      4      |       5       |
| Hobby         | card-games | skydiving | writing    | baking      | rock-climbing |
| Birthday   | may     | october   | april     | july | january    |
| Flower   | balloon-flower  | aconite  | begonia     | azalea       | bellflower     |
| Game     | poker       | go     | domino | whist       | bridge          |

 